title: DANIA BEACH 1 BEDROOM WATER VIEW APARTMENT
posting_body: ['LISTING ID 1079879', 'This apartment located in a mid-rise rental community in Dania Beach features elevated ceilings, lake views, a private balcony, spacious and walk-in closets, wall-to-wall carpeting, and a fully equipped kitchen with a dishwasher.', 'Enjoy the comforts of off-street parking, central A/C, and in-unit laundry.', 'The gated community offers two charcoal grills with seating area, a 24-hour fitness center, elevators, a large swimming pool with sundeck and lounge seating, wine and cheese events and food trucks, clubhouse, and WiFi in the common areas.', 'Concierge fees include water, sewage, trash, pest control and 24 hour package system.', 'Deleaded and pet-friendly.', 'Located within a ten-minute drive of I-95, Ft Lauderdale Airport, and local shopping and dining options.', 'LISTING ID 1079879', '*PLEASE REFERENCE ABOVE LISTING ID', 'WHEN INQUIRING*', 'Stop searching.', 'You’ve already come to the right place.', 'If you’re looking for ANY type of property whether it’s a studio, an apartment, a townhouse or single family home...', 'YES WE GOT IT.', 'We’re a ONE STOP shop that can assist you in taking the next step towards your next home today.', 'No one makes it this easy!', 'Just send us a text to', 'show contact info', 'with your name and we can send you a CUSTOM list of properties that match what you’re looking for and get the process started.', 'Thank you!', 'Konrad', '*DISCLAIMER - We do post properties for a 30 day period of time.', 'Due to High Rental Demand, some properties advertised may be withdrawn, cancelled, rented, pending or sold within the past 30 days.', 'All information is deemed to be correct, but not guaranteed*']
